Part of the coding style in Gazebo is to open curly braces in a new line as follows:

~~~
  if (condition)
  {
    // content with 2 space indentation
  }

  for (condition)
  {
    // content with 2 space indentation
  } 
~~~

All the constant variables should start with `k`. E.g.:

```
#!c++
static const std::string kBeforeKickOff;

```

Let's create a gazebo namespace:

```
#!c++
namespace gazebo
{
```
